title: I'm a (MF) Computer
tags: 2011 Annoying Evoke Lyrics-Incomplete modem Speech-Synth vocoder
info:
Ranked 2nd in the mp3/ogg music compo at Evoke 2011.
Lyrics:

I'm a lyrical virus, I am infecting your brain
you're puny little humans, i'm ahead of your game

i'm a motherfucking computer, I'm like [bleep]

whereever you go - i already know

like the weight of your mom, that's way too huge
bitches really love me because they think i'm cute
